  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Defined echo/elastography benignity criteria</measure>
    <time_frame>two and half years</time_frame>
    <description>For ultrasound and elastography benignity criteria which will be retained, outcome focus on cytoponctions number for benin nodules can be avoided by taking into account this benign criteria</description>
  </primary_outcome>
